---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Business Loan - Apply Online @ 14% p.a. | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <a href="#">Loans</a>
        <span><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span class="current">Business Loan</span>
      </nav>
      <h1>Business Loan</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Grow your business with affordable financing starting at just <strong>14% p.a.</strong> Compare offers from top banks and NBFCs, and get funds up to ₹5 Crore with flexible repayment options.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i>
          <span>Loan Amount: ₹1L - ₹5Cr</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
          <span>Tenure: 1-5 Years</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-percent"></i>
          <span>Interest: 14% onwards</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">

          <!-- Overview -->
          <div class="content-section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <span class="section-tag">Overview</span>
              <h2>What is a Business Loan?</h2>
            </div>
            <p>A business loan is a financial product designed to help entrepreneurs, small business owners, and enterprises meet their funding requirements. Whether you need capital for expansion, purchasing equipment, managing working capital, or launching a new venture, a business loan provides the necessary financial support without diluting your ownership.</p>
            <p>At TrueCred Loan Expert, we partner with India's leading banks and NBFCs to bring you the best business loan offers. With interest rates starting at just 14% p.a. and loan amounts up to ₹5 Crore, you can find the perfect financing solution tailored to your business needs. Our streamlined application process ensures quick approvals and fast disbursals so your business never has to wait.</p>

            <div class="info-grid">
              <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-percent"></i></div>
                <div class="info-box-content">
                  <span class="info-label">Interest Rate</span>
                  <strong class="info-value">14% p.a. onwards</strong>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i></div>
                <div class="info-box-content">
                  <span class="info-label">Loan Amount</span>
                  <strong class="info-value">Up to ₹5 Crore</strong>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i></div>
                <div class="info-box-content">
                  <span class="info-label">Tenure</span>
                  <strong class="info-value">Up to 5 Years</strong>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Interest Rate Table -->
          <div class="content-section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <span class="section-tag">Compare Rates</span>
              <h2>Business Loan Interest Rates 2026</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Compare business loan interest rates from India's top banks and NBFCs. These rates are indicative and may vary based on your business profile, turnover, credit score, and loan amount.</p>
            <div class="table-responsive">
              <table class="rate-table">
                <thead>
                  <tr>
                    <th>Bank / NBFC</th>
                    <th>Interest Rate (p.a.)</th>
                    <th>Loan Amount</th>
                    <th>Max Tenure</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>SBI</strong></td>
                    <td>14.50% onwards</td>
                    <td>Up to ₹5 Crore</td>
                    <td>5 Years</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>HDFC Bank</strong></td>
                    <td>14.00% onwards</td>
                    <td>Up to ₹50 Lakh</td>
                    <td>4 Years</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>ICICI Bank</strong></td>
                    <td>15.00% onwards</td>
                    <td>Up to ₹2 Crore</td>
                    <td>5 Years</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Axis Bank</strong></td>
                    <td>14.25% onwards</td>
                    <td>Up to ₹50 Lakh</td>
                    <td>5 Years</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td><strong>Bajaj Finserv</strong></td>
                    <td>14.99% onwards</td>
                    <td>Up to ₹80 Lakh</td>
                    <td>5 Years</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Types of Business Loans -->
          <div class="content-section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <span class="section-tag">Loan Types</span>
              <h2>Types of Business Loans</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Business loans come in various forms to suit different needs and stages of your business. Here are the most popular types of business loans available in India:</p>

            <div class="info-grid">
              <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-industry"></i></div>
                <div class="info-box-content">
                  <strong class="info-value">MSME Loan</strong>
                  <span class="info-label">Tailored for micro, small, and medium enterprises with government-backed schemes like MUDRA and CGTMSE. Get collateral-free loans up to ₹2 Crore at subsidized rates.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-money-bill-trend-up"></i></div>
                <div class="info-box-content">
                  <strong class="info-value">Working Capital Loan</strong>
                  <span class="info-label">Short-term financing to manage day-to-day operational expenses including inventory, payroll, rent, and other recurring costs. Keep your cash flow healthy and business running smoothly.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-store"></i></div>
                <div class="info-box-content">
                  <strong class="info-value">Small Business Loan</strong>
                  <span class="info-label">Designed for small businesses and startups looking for quick funding without extensive documentation. Ideal for shop owners, traders, and small-scale manufacturers.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-box">
                <div class="info-box-icon"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div>
                <div class="info-box-content">
                  <strong class="info-value">Startup Loan</strong>
                  <span class="info-label">Special financing programs for new businesses and startups with innovative ideas. Available under government initiatives like Startup India with relaxed eligibility criteria.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Eligibility -->
          <div class="content-section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <span class="section-tag">Eligibility</span>
              <h2>Business Loan Eligibility Criteria</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Meeting the eligibility criteria increases your chances of quick loan approval. While requirements may vary across lenders, here are the general eligibility conditions for a business loan:</p>

            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Business Vintage</strong>
                  <span>Your business should be operational for at least 1-3 years (varies by lender). Startups may qualify under special schemes.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Annual Turnover</strong>
                  <span>Minimum annual turnover of ₹10 Lakh to ₹1 Crore depending on the lender and loan amount applied for.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Credit Score</strong>
                  <span>A CIBIL score of 700 or above is generally preferred. Some lenders may consider applicants with a score of 650+.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Business Type</strong>
                  <span>Sole proprietorships, partnerships, LLPs, private limited companies, and self-employed professionals are eligible.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Age of Applicant</strong>
                  <span>The applicant should be between 21 and 65 years of age at the time of loan application.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Profitable Business</strong>
                  <span>The business should be generating consistent profits with positive cash flow as reflected in the financial statements.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- How to Apply -->
          <div class="content-section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <span class="section-tag">How to Apply</span>
              <h2>How to Apply for a Business Loan</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Applying for a business loan with TrueCred Loan Expert is simple and quick. Follow these four easy steps to get your business funded:</p>

            <div class="steps-grid">
              <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <h4>Check Eligibility</h4>
                <p>Fill in your basic business details and check your eligibility instantly. Get matched with the best lenders for your profile.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
                <h4>Compare Offers</h4>
                <p>Review and compare loan offers from multiple banks and NBFCs. Choose the one with the best interest rate and terms.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">3</div>
                <h4>Submit Documents</h4>
                <p>Upload your business documents online including KYC, financial statements, and bank statements for quick verification.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">4</div>
                <h4>Get Funded</h4>
                <p>Once approved, the loan amount is disbursed directly to your business bank account within 24-72 hours.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Documents Required -->
          <div class="content-section">
            <div class="section-header">
              <span class="section-tag">Documentation</span>
              <h2>Documents Required for Business Loan</h2>
            </div>
            <p>Keep these documents ready for a smooth and fast loan application process. Requirements may vary slightly across lenders:</p>

            <ul class="feature-list">
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-file-lines"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Identity Proof</strong>
                  <span>PAN Card, Aadhaar Card, Passport, or Voter ID of all business owners and partners.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-file-lines"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Address Proof</strong>
                  <span>Aadhaar Card, Utility Bill, Rental Agreement, or Property Ownership documents.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-file-lines"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Business Proof</strong>
                  <span>GST Registration, Udyam Registration, Shop &amp; Establishment Certificate, or Trade License.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-file-lines"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Financial Statements</strong>
                  <span>Last 2 years' audited Balance Sheet, Profit &amp; Loss Statement, and Income Tax Returns (ITR).</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-file-lines"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Bank Statements</strong>
                  <span>Last 12 months' bank statements of the business's primary operating account.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <i class="fas fa-file-lines"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong>Business Plan (for Startups)</strong>
                  <span>A detailed business plan with financial projections if applying under startup loan schemes.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside class="content-sidebar">

          <!-- Quick Apply Form -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Quick Apply</h3>
            <p>Get personalized business loan offers in minutes</p>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label>Business Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Enter your business name" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label>Mobile Number</label>
                <input type="tel" class="form-input" placeholder="Enter 10-digit mobile number" maxlength="10" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label>Loan Amount</label>
                <select class="form-input">
                  <option value="">Select Loan Amount</option>
                  <option value="5">Up to ₹5 Lakh</option>
                  <option value="10">₹5 Lakh - ₹10 Lakh</option>
                  <option value="25">₹10 Lakh - ₹25 Lakh</option>
                  <option value="50">₹25 Lakh - ₹50 Lakh</option>
                  <option value="100">₹50 Lakh - ₹1 Crore</option>
                  <option value="500">₹1 Crore - ₹5 Crore</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label>Annual Turnover</label>
                <select class="form-input">
                  <option value="">Select Annual Turnover</option>
                  <option value="10">Up to ₹10 Lakh</option>
                  <option value="25">₹10 Lakh - ₹25 Lakh</option>
                  <option value="50">₹25 Lakh - ₹50 Lakh</option>
                  <option value="100">₹50 Lakh - ₹1 Crore</option>
                  <option value="500">₹1 Crore - ₹5 Crore</option>
                  <option value="1000">Above ₹5 Crore</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">
                Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
              <p class="form-disclaimer">
                <i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Your data is 100% safe &amp; secure
              </p>
            </form>
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Links -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-link"></i> Quick Links</h3>
            <ul class="sidebar-links">
              <li><a href="/pages/personal-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Personal Loan</a></li>
              <li><a href="/pages/home-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Home Loan</a></li>
              <li><a href="/pages/loan-against-property"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Loan Against Property</a></li>
              <li><a href="/pages/gold-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Gold Loan</a></li>
              <li><a href="/pages/education-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Education Loan</a></li>
              <li><a href="/pages/car-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Car Loan</a></li>
              <li><a href="/pages/credit-cards"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Credit Cards</a></li>
              <li><a href="/pages/credit-score"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Credit Score</a></li>
              <li><a href="/pages/calculators"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> EMI Calculator</a></li>
              <li><a href="/pages/insurance"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Insurance</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </aside>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">FAQs</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Find answers to common questions about business loans</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <span>What is the minimum eligibility for a business loan?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              <p>To be eligible for a business loan, your business should typically be operational for at least 1-3 years with a minimum annual turnover of ₹10 Lakh. The applicant should be between 21-65 years old with a CIBIL score of 650 or above. However, eligibility criteria may vary across different banks and NBFCs. Some lenders also offer loans to newer businesses under special MSME and startup schemes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <span>What is the maximum amount I can get as a business loan?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              <p>The maximum business loan amount depends on the lender, your business turnover, profitability, and creditworthiness. Generally, you can get a business loan ranging from ₹1 Lakh to ₹5 Crore. Banks like SBI offer up to ₹5 Crore for established businesses, while NBFCs like Bajaj Finserv offer up to ₹80 Lakh. The loan amount is typically capped at a percentage of your annual turnover.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I get a business loan without collateral?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              <p>Yes, many banks and NBFCs offer unsecured (collateral-free) business loans. Under the CGTMSE scheme, loans up to ₹2 Crore are available without any collateral or third-party guarantee. Most lenders offer unsecured business loans up to ₹50 Lakh based on your business financials and credit score. For higher amounts, lenders may require property or other assets as security.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <span>How long does it take to get a business loan approved?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              <p>The approval timeline for a business loan varies by lender and loan type. For unsecured business loans from NBFCs, approval can happen within 24-48 hours with disbursal in 2-3 working days. Bank loans may take 5-7 working days for processing and approval. Through TrueCred Loan Expert, you can fast-track your application with pre-approved offers and get funds disbursed within 24-72 hours of approval.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <span>What are the tax benefits on a business loan?</span>
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              <p>The interest paid on a business loan is tax-deductible as a business expense under Section 36(1)(iii) of the Income Tax Act. This means the interest component of your EMI can be claimed as a deduction against your business income, effectively reducing your tax liability. However, the principal repayment is not eligible for tax deduction. It is advisable to consult a tax professional for specific tax planning advice.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page CTA -->
  <section class="page-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to Grow Your Business?</h2>
        <p>Get instant business loan offers from top banks and NBFCs. Apply now and receive funds in your account within 24-72 hours.</p>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
            <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Apply Now
          </a>
          <a href="/pages/contact" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">
            <i class="fas fa-headset"></i> Talk to Expert
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
